 he is not the worst at value. 12. SATTRIYA failed to fire as the favourite 5 weeks ago, and tries 1600m for the first time. Don't risk her.\",\"runners\":[1,3,7,4,12],\"exclusive\":true}","tips":{"tipType":"Standard","tipster":"NZ TAB","tipRunnerNumbers":[10,7,3,12]},"ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,3,5,4]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[7,4,1,3]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,3,12,6]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[7,12,6,1]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[12,7,2,3]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[5,1,3,2]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,7,3,12]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"OTK","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"OTK","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"OTK","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"OTK","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Duet","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"OTK","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Trifecta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"OTK","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"FirstFour","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"OTK","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"RunningDouble","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"OTK","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"DailyDouble","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"OTK","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quaddie","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":5,"venueMnemonic":"OTK","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Treble","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"OTK","raceType":"R"}}]}}}